# Authentication Middleware

Secure your API endpoints using JWT (JSON Web Tokens). Titan provides a built-in guard for token validation.

### Implementation

Attach the guard to your routes to enforce authentication.

```typescript
import { AuthGuard } from '@titan/auth';

@UseGuards(AuthGuard)
@Controller('/profile')
export class ProfileController {
  // Only accessible with valid token
}
```

### Custom Strategy

You can implement custom strategies by extending the base `Strategy` class.

```typescript
export class ApiKeyStrategy extends Strategy {
  validate(req: Request) {
    const key = req.headers['x-api-key'];
    if (!key) throw new UnauthorizedError();
    return { id: key };
  }
}
```

